                                <div class="post-date">March 18, 2026</div>
                                <h1 class="post-title">Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip</h1>
                                <div class="excerpt">
                                    <input class="jpibfi" type="hidden"><p><em>Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip.</em></p>
                                </div>
                                                                    <div class="recipetimes">
                                                                                    <div><div class="rt-label">Prep Time</div><div class="rt-value">5 mins</div></div>
                                                                                                                            <div><div class="rt-label">Cook Time</div><div class="rt-value">0 mins</div></div>
                                                                                                                            <div><div class="rt-label">Total Time</div><div class="rt-value">5 mins</div></div>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                <div class="dmc-amazon-disclosure"><p>This post may contain affiliate links, which means that I make a small commission off items you purchase at no additional cost to you. Please read my <a href="/privacy-policy/">policy page</a>.</p></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="dmc-col-2">
                                <div class="dmc-col-inner">
                                    <a href="#wprm-recipe-container-94352" data-recipe="94352" style="color: #333333;" class="wprm-recipe-jump wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal">Jump to Recipe</a>                                    <div class="dmc-image-holder">
                                        <img width="594" height="594" src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-594x594.jpg" class="attachment-single-featured size-single-featured" alt="red pepper feta dip in a bowl with pita crackers" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-594x594.jpg 594w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-277x277.jpg 277w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-554x554.jpg 554w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-273x273.jpg 273w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-546x546.jpg 546w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-375x375.jpg 375w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-750x750.jpg 750w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-603x603.jpg 603w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-69x69.jpg 69w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-138x138.jpg 138w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-279x279.jpg 279w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-558x558.jpg 558w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-170x170.jpg 170w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-340x340.jpg 340w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 594px) 100vw, 594px" data-pin-description="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." data-pin-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/?tp_image_id=94383" />                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="dmc-single-post-content">
                            <div class="not-sidebar">
                                <div class="dmc-content-inner content f-links-with-shadow">
                                    <input class="jpibfi" type="hidden"><p><span id="more-94351"></span></p>
<p>I made you a savory, spicy feta dip blended up to creamy perfection. Get your crackers and veggies ready for this perfect, easy snack or appetizer.</p>
<p>This spicy roasted <strong>red pepper feta dip</strong> is inspired by traditional Greek htipiti, and WOW, the flavors are out-of-this-world delicious. For dinners lately, I&#8217;ve been obsessed with creating hearty bowls with protein, veggies, a yummy grain, and a unique sauce to pull it all together. This dip is actually the base of my super satisfying, <a title="Spiced Mediterranean Chicken Bowls" href="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/spiced-mediterranean-chicken-bowls/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spiced Mediterranean Chicken Bowls</a>!</p>
<p>Add this to your snack rotation, serve it up as an easy appetizer the next time you&#8217;re hosting, or spread it on a sandwich or wrap to give it extra flavor. Anyway you enjoy this dip or spread, I guarantee you&#8217;ll LOVE it.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/?tp_image_id=94380" data-pin-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" class="lazyload aligncenter wp-image-94380 size-full" title="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." src="data:image/svg+xml,&lt;svg xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 1067 1600&quot;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4.jpg" alt="dipping a carrot into roasted red pepper dip" width="1067" height="1600" data-pin-description="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4.jpg 1067w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-100x150.jpg 100w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-273x410.jpg 273w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-546x820.jpg 546w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-372x558.jpg 372w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-744x1116.jpg 744w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-708x1062.jpg 708w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-582x873.jpg 582w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-458x687.jpg 458w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-916x1374.jpg 916w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-306x459.jpg 306w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-612x918.jpg 612w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-139x208.jpg 139w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-277x416.jpg 277w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-694x1041.jpg 694w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-216x324.jpg 216w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-432x648.jpg 432w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" /><noscript><img decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/?tp_image_id=94380" data-pin-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" class="lazyload aligncenter wp-image-94380 size-full" title="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4.jpg" alt="dipping a carrot into roasted red pepper dip" width="1067" height="1600" data-pin-description="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4.jpg" srcset="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4.jpg 1067w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-100x150.jpg 100w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-273x410.jpg 273w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-546x820.jpg 546w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-372x558.jpg 372w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-744x1116.jpg 744w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-708x1062.jpg 708w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-582x873.jpg 582w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-458x687.jpg 458w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-916x1374.jpg 916w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-306x459.jpg 306w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-612x918.jpg 612w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-139x208.jpg 139w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-277x416.jpg 277w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-694x1041.jpg 694w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-216x324.jpg 216w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-432x648.jpg 432w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-4-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" /></noscript></p>
<h2>Ingredients in this spicy red pepper feta dip</h2>
<p>As I mentioned, this creamy dip requires just 6 simple ingredients, but it&#8217;s absolutely bursting with flavor. Here&#8217;s what you&#8217;ll need:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Feta:</strong> I love using feta cheese as the base for dip recipes because it adds plenty of salty, savory flavor.</li>
<li><strong>Roasted red peppers:</strong> the key ingredient? A jar of <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0omVZoA2Av7" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">roasted red bell peppers</a>! We&#8217;re not roasting our own bell pepper for this recipe. You can typically find these jars near the artichokes, olives, etc. Feel free to use regular or fire-roasted.</li>
<li><strong>Garlic:</strong> you&#8217;ll need a clove of fresh garlic for savory flavor.</li>
<li><strong>Lemon juice:</strong> add the perfect amount of brightness with a little lemon juice or red wine vinegar.</li>
<li><strong>Olive oil:</strong> a touch of <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0394FYGu28z" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">olive oil</a> helps blend everything together so it&#8217;s nice and smooth.</li>
<li><strong>Red pepper flakes:</strong> add a delicious kick of heat with <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0uSM3yu6ef0" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">red pepper flakes</a>! See below for more ways to up the spice level.</li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" data-pin-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/?tp_image_id=94377" data-pin-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" class="lazyload aligncenter wp-image-94377 size-full" title="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." src="data:image/svg+xml,&lt;svg xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 1067 1600&quot;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1.jpg" alt="ingredients for red pepper feta dip in a food processor" width="1067" height="1600" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1.jpg 1067w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-100x150.jpg 100w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-273x410.jpg 273w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-546x820.jpg 546w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-372x558.jpg 372w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-744x1116.jpg 744w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-708x1062.jpg