his wonderful dip." src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1.jpg" alt="ingredients for red pepper feta dip in a food processor" width="1067" height="1600" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1.jpg" srcset="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1.jpg 1067w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-100x150.jpg 100w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-273x410.jpg 273w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-546x820.jpg 546w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-372x558.jpg 372w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-744x1116.jpg 744w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-708x1062.jpg 708w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-582x873.jpg 582w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-458x687.jpg 458w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-916x1374.jpg 916w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-306x459.jpg 306w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-612x918.jpg 612w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-139x208.jpg 139w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-277x416.jpg 277w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-694x1041.jpg 694w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-216x324.jpg 216w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-432x648.jpg 432w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-1-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" /></noscript></p>
<h2>Can I make it dairy-free?</h2>
<p>The feta cheese base is really what makes this dip, but you can try subbing dairy-free feta crumbles if you can find them! I haven&#8217;t tested it, so I&#8217;m not 100% certain on the flavor, but let me know in the comments if you do.</p>
