 wonderful dip." src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2.jpg" alt="easy roasted red pepper feta dip in a food processor" width="1067" height="1600" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt="" data-jpibfi-post-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/" data-jpibfi-post-title="Spicy Roasted Red Pepper Feta Dip" data-jpibfi-src="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2.jpg" srcset="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2.jpg 1067w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-100x150.jpg 100w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-273x410.jpg 273w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-546x820.jpg 546w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-372x558.jpg 372w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-744x1116.jpg 744w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-708x1062.jpg 708w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-582x873.jpg 582w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-458x687.jpg 458w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-916x1374.jpg 916w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-306x459.jpg 306w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-612x918.jpg 612w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-139x208.jpg 139w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-277x416.jpg 277w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-694x1041.jpg 694w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-216x324.jpg 216w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-432x648.jpg 432w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-760x1140.jpg 760w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-2-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" /></noscript></p>
<h2>Choose your spice level</h2>
<p>If you don&#8217;t have red pepper flakes, try blending in a jalapeño or a spicy red pepper to give the dip a lovely kick of heat!</p>
<p>Alternatively, if you&#8217;re serving kiddos or are sensitive to spice, simply omit the red pepper flakes.</p>
<h2>Easy roasted red pepper feta dip in 3 steps</h2>
<ol>
<li>Add all of the dip ingredients to the bowl of a <a href="https://amzlink.to/az02G68j6wEhd" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">food processor</a>.</li>
<li>Process the dip on high for about 1 minute, scraping down the sides with a <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0a6fPdTD6rd" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">little spatula</a> as needed, until it&#8217;s nice and creamy.</li>
<li>Serve it in <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0RMLRdhhOF9" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">shallow bowls</a> with anything your heart desires! See below for delicious ideas.</li>
</ol>
