<h2>Storing tips</h2>
<p>Store any leftover roasted red pepper feta dip in an <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0S7FiqGmqke" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">airtight container</a> in the fridge for up to 4-5 days.</p>
<h2>Tools you&#8217;ll need</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://amzlink.to/az02G68j6wEhd" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Food processor</a></li>
<li><a href="https://amzlink.to/az0a6fPdTD6rd" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Spatula</a></li>
<li><a href="https://amzlink.to/az0RMLRdhhOF9" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">Shallow serving bowls</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Get all of my favorite kitchen tools <a href="https://amzlink.to/az0URjyH3n1FW" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">here</a>!</p>
