oasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-375x375.jpg 375w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-750x750.jpg 750w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-603x603.jpg 603w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-594x594.jpg 594w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-69x69.jpg 69w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-138x138.jpg 138w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-279x279.jpg 279w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-558x558.jpg 558w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-340x340.jpg 340w, https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Spicy-Roasted-Red-Pepper-Feta-Dip-6-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 170px) 100vw, 170px" data-pin-description="Creamy, spicy roasted red pepper feta dip made with six simple ingredients easily blended right in your food processor. This savory red pepper dip not only makes a delicious appetizer or snack with pita chips, veggies, and crackers but is also the perfect spread on sandwiches or wraps! Add a kick of heat to your charcuterie board or lunch with this wonderful dip." data-pin-url="https://www.ambitiouskitchen.com/red-pepper-feta-dip/?tp_image_id=94383" /></noscript></div>
